        <div class="main review-item" id="1025336">

            
    
    <header class="main-hd">
        <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/breezee/" class="avator">
            <img width="24" height="24" src="https://img2.doubanio.com/icon/u1000108-1.jpg">
        </a>

        <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/breezee/" class="name">小小风也</a>

            <span class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>

        <span content="2006-02-11" class="main-meta">2006-02-11 11:45:38</span>


    </header>


            <div class="main-bd">

                <h2><a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1025336/">一本好书，一个有负众望的译本</a></h2>

                <div id="review_1025336_short" class="review-short" data-rid="1025336">
                    <div class="short-content">
                            <p class="spoiler-tip">这篇书评可能有关键情节透露</p>

                        吃惊地发现任溶溶版＜夏洛的网＞在豆瓣广受好评。我相信有些朋友和我一样，认识得到任版的问题，但无意介入这场文字之争，或碍于出版界和译者的情面，放弃了表达的权利。但最让一个爱书人郁闷的事，是一本绝品级的书，被不恰当地表达，不恰当地阅读，甚至不恰当地赞美和传播下...

                        &nbsp;(<a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1025336-copy" class="unfold" title="展开">展开</a>)
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div id="review_1025336_full" class="hidden">
                    <div id="review_1025336_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
                </div>

                <div class="action">
                    <a href="javascript:;" class="action-btn up" data-rid="1025336" title="有用">
